Text: I Think This Album is Great!...  Thanks! I'm Seeding Right Now....
Just heard 'Forsaker' on the radio and it was pretty good, so I'm gonna check this out.  It reminds me a little of Opeth.

Quite possibly one of the greatest albums to ever come out of the Swedish Metal Scene.

A truly amazing album. Def buy this one for real. 

10/10
great album and fast download speed
